Who I Am

I’m Emmanuel Ubah — a product-focused builder passionate about technology, real estate, and creating solutions built in Africa that can scale globally.

What I Do

I work as a project manager, building and documenting features for real estate digital products.

My Background

I’m originally from Anambra State, Nigeria, and currently live in Lagos.
